{"word":"H3835 - לָבַן - lâban - law-ban' - Make brick","slug":"H3835","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">לָבַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>lâban"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>law-ban'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Make brick"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DC;&#x05D1;&#x05DF; - la&#x0302;ban</b> - <i>law-ban'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>be</i> (or <i>become</i>) <i>white</i>; also (as denominative from <a href=\"#/H3843\">H3843</a>) to <i>make bricks: - </i>make brick, be (made, make) white (-r)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3828\">H3828</a>, <a href=\"#/H3829\">H3829</a>, <a href=\"#/H3836\">H3836</a>, <a href=\"#/H3837\">H3837</a>, <a href=\"#/H3838\">H3838</a>, <a href=\"#/H3839\">H3839</a>, <a href=\"#/H3840\">H3840</a>, <a href=\"#/H3841\">H3841</a>, <a href=\"#/H3842\">H3842</a>, <a href=\"#/H3843\">H3843</a>, <a href=\"#/H3844\">H3844</a>, <a href=\"#/H3845\">H3845</a>, <a href=\"#/H3846\">H3846</a>, <a href=\"#/H4192\">H4192</a>, <a href=\"#/H4404\">H4404</a>"}]}